					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really loved the fact that this SCP used to be a library and how information regarding this SCP is how it used to be a library. However, I don't like the fact that it used to be a library and how it is a former library. Also, it is very unsettling, personally, for how its anti-memetic effects function with how it used to be a library. The images of this former library really made it interesting to me, despite how it used to be a library. Definitely deserves a rating of +1, since it's a former library.</p> 
				 	]]>
