					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1232784#post-3559299</guid>
				<title>Re: Just confirming</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1232784/scp-2602-which-used-to-be-a-library#post-3559299</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2017 21:14:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Khaim</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1796098</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Best explained by the last line:</p> <blockquote> <p>This likely served to highlight the fact that SCP-2602 used to be a library and obscure the SCP-2602 used to be a library.</p> </blockquote> <p>The first half of this is what the agent intended to write. SCP-2602 was a library from 1921-06-08 to 1988-04-29. The ungrammatical second half is the SCP-2602 used to be a library.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
