								<wikidot:authorUserId>1875764</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Did someone change the title of this? I could have sworn that the title was originally:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-2602, which used to be a library</p> </blockquote> <p>But now it's:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-2602 - Exbibliothetic</p> </blockquote> <p>Is this intentional? Was it only changed recently? Was it vandalised? Further more; it doesn't make any reference to being a former library, so it doesn't even make sense.</p> <p>So yeah&#8230;I'd appreciate knowing this. Especially since I was trying to search for this on the Series 3 page by using the good old cntrl+f and typing in &quot;library&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
